    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Neotropical Scolopini (Hemiptera: Heteroptera: Anthocoridae): new taxa, diagnostic characters and a key to the genera of the tribe" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330423>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330419>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330427>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330425>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330431> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330423>
    dc:description "Figs. 10–15. Guayascoris foreroi gen.& sp. nov.10–14 – holotype, male: 10 – head; 11 – fore tibia; 12 – hemelytron; 13 – abdominal uradenia; 14a – pygophore; 14b – detail of left paramere. 15 – paratype, female, abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5330423/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330419>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–9. 1 – Calliodis pallescens (Reuter, 1884); 2 – Eulasiocolpus megalops Champion, 1900; 3 – Guayascoris foreroi gen. & sp. nov.; 4 – Lepidonannella opaca (Poppius, 1909); 5 – Nidicola mitra Drake & Herring, 1964; 6 – Opisthypselus punctaticollis Reuter, 1908; 7 – Zopherocoris armatus (Stål, 1860); 8 – Scolopella brasiliensis Carayon, 1954; 9 – Scolopocoris gracilicornis (Poppius, 1909). Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5330419/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330427>
    dc:description "Figs. 22–27.22 – Nidicola mitra Drake & Herring, 1964, ostiolar peritreme; 23 – Opisthypselus punctaticollis Reuter, 1909, ostiolar peritreme; 24, 25 – Zopherocoris armatus Reuter, 1871; 24 – fore femora; 25 – ostiolar peritreme; 26, 27 – Scolopella brasiliensis Carayon, 1954; 26 – ostiolar peritreme; 27 – detail of evaporatorium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5330427/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330425>
    dc:description "Figs. 16–21. 16 – Calliodis pallescens Reuter, 1884, ostiolar peritreme. 17, 18 – Eulasiocolpus megalops Champion, 1900: 17 – ostiolar peritreme; 18 – detail of evaporatorium. 19–21 – Lepidonannella opaca (Poppius, 1909): 19 – scales on pronotum; 20 – ostiolar peritreme, 21 – detail of evaporatorium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5330425/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5330431>
    dc:description "Figs. 28–30. Scolopocoris gracilicornis (Poppius, 1909). 28 – fore femora; 29 – ostiolar peritreme; 30 – detail of evaporatorium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5330431/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

